    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine Patris et Filii et Spiritu Sancti. Anni hab incarnacione domini
                        nostri Iesu Christi millesimo nonagesimo tercio, domni <persName
                            key="#Popes" ref="#people/4301">Clementi</persName> pape sede anno
                        decimo, imperante domnus <persName key="#Emperor/king" ref="#people/77"
                            >Henricus</persName> filius quondam Henrici imperatori anno similiter
                        decimo, die tercio mensis madio, ind(icione) prima, in <placeName
                            ref="#places/4179">Pomposea</placeName>. Petistis a nos quidem in Dei
                        nomine domnus <persName key="#Abbots" ref="#people/1599"
                            >Geronimus</persName> gr(aci)a Dei <rs key="#Abbots">abbas</rs> regule
                            <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterii</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Confinia #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos #Massae #Landed_possessions #Forests #Fisheries #Penalty #Cereals #Maiores #Legumes #Wine #Hay/fodder #Linen #Poultry #Books #Exenia #Land_clearing #Fluvial_transport #Levies #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters #Monasteries"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1460">Sancte Marie qui vocatur in <placeName
                                ref="#places/4179">Pomposea</placeName></orgName> cum consensum
                        deserviencium eiusdem monasterii ordinatore, uti nobis in Dei nomine
                                <persName><name ref="Iohannes de Berga"> Iohannes qui vocatur de
                                Berga</name></persName> et <persName><name ref="Dominicus"
                                >Dominicus</name></persName> sitque <persName><name ref="Margarita"
                                >Margarita</name></persName> nepoti tui petitori in tres vero parte
                        de res que in inferius legitu et <rs key="#Casalia">casale</rs> cum <rs
                            key="#Wine">vinea</rs>, ubi vos habitare visi estis, et in alia vero
                        parte petitori <persName><name ref="Wido">Uuitho</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name ref="Astrigunda">Astrigunda</name></persName> cognus
                        sua et <persName><name ref="Iuliana">Iiuliana</name></persName> sorore
                        vestra et <persName><name ref="Teobaldus">Tebaldo</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name ref="Gaudiosa">Gaudiosa</name></persName> cognus sua
                        sitque <persName><name ref="Biligunda">Biligunda</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name ref="Petrus">Petrus</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name ref="Digna">Dinna</name></persName> iugale sua,
                        germano et cognus, toti petitoris unusquisque persecutare debeatis singulis
                        in vestris porcionibus, secundum quod intra vos iuste et dividere debeatis
                        seu filii et heredibus, <rs key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis"> llibellu
                            nomine</rs> concedimus et largimus atque confirmamus vobis de rem iuris
                        suprascripto monasterio nostro, idest omnes res et porcione vestra
                        int(e)g(ras) quantascumque abuit et detinuit vel pertinuit a quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Petrus de Berga"> Petrus qui vocatur de
                                Berga</name></persName> genitori vestro infra tota masa qui vocatur
                            <placeName
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Confinia #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos #Massae #Landed_possessions #Forests #Fisheries #Cereals #Maiores #Legumes #Wine #Hay/fodder #Linen #Poultry #Land_clearing #Fluvial_transport #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"
                            ref="#places/3559"><geogName
                                key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Confinia #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos #Massae #Landed_possessions #Forests #Fisheries #Cereals #Maiores #Legumes #Wine #Hay/fodder #Linen #Poultry #Land_clearing #Fluvial_transport #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"
                                ref="#estates/2454">Laco Sancto</geogName></placeName> per anteriore
                        llibello per singulas locas, <rs key="Confinia">interrafines</rs> de supras
                        tota masa hoc est: hab uno llatere <rs key="#Canals">fosa</rs> de <rs
                            key="#Mills">molino</rs> de <placeName
                            key="#Confinia #Mills #Canals #Fluvial_transport" ref="#places/3550"
                            >volta de Laterclo</placeName> percurente usque a medio <placeName
                            key="#Confinia #Rivers" ref="#places/3565">Aguillolo</placeName> et per
                        inde usque a medio <placeName key="#Confinia #Rivers" ref="#places/3566"
                            >Triba</placeName> perveniente usque a media <placeName key="#Confinia"
                            ref="#places/3567">Elia</placeName> et per <rs
                            key="#Marshes/lagoons/tombolos">padule</rs> usque a media <placeName
                            key="#Confinia #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos" ref="#places/3557"
                            >Curba</placeName> et ultra Curba et padule usque a <placeName
                            key="#Confinia #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos" ref="#places/4196"
                            >Pado</placeName> et ultra Pado usque a <placeName key="#Forests #Confinia" ref="#places/4877"
                            >Gazio</placeName> quod est iure de episcopio <orgName
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1498" key="#Confinia #Forests">sancte <placeName
                                ref="#places/485">Comiacliense</placeName> eclesie</orgName> et inde
                        usque a canale qui vocatur de <placeName key="#Confinia #Canals"
                            ref="#places/3568">Cesi</placeName>, hab alio latere <placeName
                            key="#Confinia" ref="#places/3569">Curlo</placeName>, fosa qui vocatur
                            <placeName key="#Confinia #Canals" ref="#places/3564">Conca
                            Agatula</placeName> desendente in <placeName key="#Confinia"
                            ref="#places/3563">Gauro</placeName> et ultra Gauro, a tercio latere
                        rivo qui vocatur <placeName
                            key="#Confinia #Rivers #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos" ref="#places/3570"
                            >Anzeli</placeName> per valle usque <placeName key="#Confinia"
                            ref="#places/3562">Masenzathega</placeName> us ad <placeName
                            key="#Confinia" ref="#places/3561">Montiselli</placeName> et per
                            <placeName key="#Confinia" ref="#places/3571">Vethathosa</placeName>
                        desendente in Patho, a quarto latere <placeName key="#Confinia"
                            ref="#places/3551">Vacoline</placeName> et <placeName key="#Confinia"
                            ref="#places/3574">argiele qui vocatur Malo</placeName> desendente in
                        calle qui vocatur <placeName key="#Confinia" ref="#places/3573"
                            >Vincareta</placeName> desendente in Laterclo. Que omnia cum <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">terris</rs> et <rs key="#Wine">vineis</rs>,
                            <rs key="#Cereals">campis</rs>, <rs key="#Hay/fodder">pratis</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Hay/fodder">pasculis</rs>, <rs key="#Forests">silvis</rs>,
                            <rs>salectis</rs>, <rs key="#Marshes/lagoons/tombolos">padulibus</rs>,
                            <rs key="#Fisheries">piscacionibus</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters">venacionibus</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters">aucupacionibus</rs> sito
                            <rs key="#Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters">capellacionibus</rs>
                        suis cum ingresu et egresu suo et cum omnibus que a suprascripta res
                        pertinentibus vel subiacentibus sicut superius legitur, heas abendum,
                        tenendum, posidendum, laborandum, roncandum, suprasedendum, defensandum et
                        in omnibus meliorandum in annis vinti a renovandum, salva call(ciaria)
                        domnica dandum llibellu renovetur. Ita sane ut inferatis Domni racionibus
                        vobis vestrisque filiis et heredibus a nobis nostrisque sucexoribus redere
                        debeatis singulis quibusque anni, hoc est <rs key="#Levies">terratico</rs>
                        de <rs key="#Cereals #Maiores">grano</rs> et <rs key="#Cereals #Maiores"
                            >sicale</rs> in campo capa quinta, <rs key="#Legumes">faba</rs> modio
                        quinto et de omni alio labore in area modio sesto, <rs key="#Linen"
                            >llino</rs> manna sesta; et si vinea pastinaveritis extra casale, postea
                        pertica pervenerit fruere debeatis annos tres, postea redere debeatis anfora
                        quarte, semel vice arbore pecto ponendo, postea sit vobis relicum concexum;
                        et si <rs key="#Land_clearing">ronco roncaveritis</rs> vel <rs
                            key="#Land_clearing">de valle terra scuseritis</rs>, fruere debeatis
                        annos tres postea redere debeatis sicut supra legitur; <rs key="#Exenia"
                            >exenio</rs> vero pro ipsi casali per in anteriore llibelli relegitur
                        dare debeatis omnique anno de grano staria duabus et <rs key="#Poultry"
                            >galine</rs> due; tritulatus et pervectus ipso terratico et ipso exenio
                        per vos usque a Laterclo ubi <rs key="#Fluvial_transport">nave nostra
                            domnica</rs> potuerit pervenire a tolendum. Pro eo quia exinde accepi,
                        call(ciarii) nomine, idest <rs key="#Books">llibrum</rs> unum pro <rs
                            key="#Price">denarii Veroniense solidos treginta</rs>. Maiore quidem
                        domino vel nostra dominacione cum onore et obediencia susipere debeatis, cum
                        fide et puritate seu umilitate sine aliqua fraude vel dolo. Si quis vero
                        pars nostra contra hoc llibellum ire temtaverimus ante perfinitum tempus
                        sicut supra legitur, det pars parti fidem servandi ante omnis litis inicium
                        vel interpell(acionis), pene nomine, <rs key="#Penalty">auri uncia una</rs>
                        et post pena soluta manead hoc llibellus in sua firmitate. Quod vero
                        llibellu una pari tinore conscripto <persName key="#Tabellio"><name
                                ref="Iohannes">Iohannem</name></persName> in Dei nomine <rs
                            key="#Tabellio">tabell(ionem)</rs> scribendum rogavi et subter manu mea
                        propria firmavi et unus alterius nobis pariter iubemus quod consecuti sumus
                        agamus Deum et nobis masimas gr(aci)a. Hieronimus abb(as) Po(m)posię
                        s(ub)s(cripsi).</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
